---
title: Hoisin Glazed Tofu Banh Mi with Rainbow Slaw
description: Sesame and hoisin glazed tofu is sandwiched inside a toasted baguette and topped with a rainbow slaw and cilantro-mayo. Bring this Vietnamese classic with a French flair into your kitchen!
